#text=Today she wants to bake a cake .
#text=She brought cake flour , sugar and cream from the supermarket .
#text=She is standing at the kitchen and ready to start .
#text=She pour three cups of flour into a large bowl .
#text=In another bowl , she separate the egg white and yolk from four eggs .
#text=She use Kitchen Aid to beat the egg white until soft peaks form and she can lift up the whip .
#text=She adds one cup of oil , half cup of sugar , egg yolk into the flour and mixed together , then she adds the egg white and mixes all together until it is well mixed .
#text=She pour the mixture into a cake baking pan and put it into the oven .
#text=After around 30 minutes , the cake is ready .
#text=She then use the cream to decorate the cake .
